Title: Is Time Travel Possible? | The Science of Doctor Who | Doctor Who | BBC
Descript: Is Time Travel really Possible? In this clip Professor Brian Cox - a confirmed Doctor Who fan - undertakes an experiment with a light showing that time moves faster for a stationary clock than a moving clock, which appears to move more slowly over the same length of time.
